{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.160", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.240", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.760", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich habe durchaus Sympathien f\u00fcr die Idee und das Ansinnen der Fraktion Die Linke, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.760", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die gesetzlichen H\u00fcrden f\u00fcr Massen\u00adentlassungen zu erh\u00f6hen,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.320", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vor allem dann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.480", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn gro\u00dfe Konzerne weltweit Gewinne erzielen und eben nicht in der Insolvenz stecken. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.560", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "J\u00fcngstes Beispiel: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.080", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "General Electric. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.640", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hier geht es einmal mehr um kurzfristige Rendite und nicht um verantwortungsbewusste Standortpolitik."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.360", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auf Kosten der Besch\u00e4ftigten sollen kurzfristig Gewinne gesteigert werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.560", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.680", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.200", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hat mit sozialer Marktwirtschaft nichts zu tun."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.960", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ob die Form des staatlichen Eingriffs, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.320", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie im Gesetzentwurf der Linksfraktion gefordert wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.880", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "verh\u00e4ltnism\u00e4\u00dfig und vor allem verfassungskonform ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.840", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "m\u00fcssen wir uns im Detail ansehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.920", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es werden \u00c4nderungen im Betriebsverfassungsgesetz, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.520", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "beim K\u00fcndigungsschutzgesetz und auch im Aktiengesetz vorgeschlagen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.800", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das sind keine Kleinigkeiten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.760", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die wir im Vorbeigehen entscheiden sollten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.920", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Diskussionen f\u00fchren wir in den Aussch\u00fcssen weiter."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.040", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.280", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Balance zwischen Mitbestimmung und unternehmerischer Freiheit muss stimmen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.560", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unternehmer sollten allerdings auch keine Angst vor Mitbestimmung haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.160", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als ehemaliger Betriebsrat wei\u00df ich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.520", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie sehr sich Besch\u00e4ftigte mit ihrem Konzern identifizieren und wie sehr sie sich um gute L\u00f6sungsvorschl\u00e4ge, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.720", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch um Kompromisse bem\u00fchen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.760", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das schadet der Unternehmensentwicklung eher selten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.440", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.440", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "oftmals kommen mir Wirtschaftsnachrichten\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.080", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "egal aus welcher Branche\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.120", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie ein Automatismus vor, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.240", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eben weil die Antwort auf Strukturwandel meistens Personalabbau und Standortschlie\u00dfung lautet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.720", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Muss das wirklich immer die Konsequenz sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.440", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "oder geht es auch anders? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.760", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gerade Gro\u00dfkonzerne, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.160", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die verschiedene Gesch\u00e4ftsfelder bedienen und finanziell solide aufgestellt sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.600", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "m\u00fcssen doch in der Lage sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.200", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ihr Personal auf neue Aufgaben vorzubereiten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.520", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um Arbeitslosigkeit und Perspektivlosigkeit zu vermeiden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.000", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich w\u00fcnsche mir an vielen Stellen mehr Unternehmerverantwortung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.920", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vor allem im Sinne der Belegschaft."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.560", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zum Unternehmertum geh\u00f6rt es, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.600", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "M\u00e4rkte zu beobachten und Produkte weiterzuentwickeln, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.360", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Menschen in Arbeit zu halten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.320", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Je nach Unternehmensgr\u00f6\u00dfe sind ganze Regionen von unternehmerischen Entscheidungen abh\u00e4ngig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.520", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ernsthafte Bem\u00fchen um bestehende Standorte fehlt mir oftmals. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.720", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Viel zu schnell ziehen gro\u00dfe Unternehmen weiter, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.920", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil anderswo g\u00fcnstiger produziert werden kann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.600", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil Steuern gespart oder Subventionen eingestrichen werden k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.520", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In meinem Wahlkreis, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.880", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "am Standort Bottrop, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.320", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und beim Kollegen Spiering in Dissen schlie\u00dfen die Feinkosthersteller Nadler und Homann aus der Unternehmensgruppe Theo M\u00fcller ihre Produktionsst\u00e4tten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.560", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.840", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit EU-Subventionen gef\u00f6rdert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.560", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nahe der deutsch-tschechischen Grenze ein neues Werk zu er\u00f6ffnen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.160", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hier werden Arbeitspl\u00e4tze vernichtet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.000", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dort werden neue zu anderen Konditionen geschaffen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.160", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist absurd."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.280", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren in den Konzernvorst\u00e4nden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.600", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zeigen Sie mehr Mut bei betriebsinternen Ausbildungen und Umschulungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.480", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zeigen Sie mehr Mut, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.000", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihre Betriebsst\u00e4tten zu ver\u00e4ndern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "188.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.920", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "anstatt sie zu schlie\u00dfen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "193.840", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Innovationen sind nicht nur im Produktbereich m\u00f6glich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "193.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.640", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es k\u00f6nnte doch auch mal soziale Innovationen in der Personalpolitik geben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "201.120", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist nicht nachvollziehbar: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "201.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.640", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Einerseits beklagen wir den Fachkr\u00e4ftemangel, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.160", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "andererseits werden Arbeitspl\u00e4tze abgebaut, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.120", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ohne die Potenziale der eigenen Belegschaft aufzudecken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.720", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ohne zu \u00fcberlegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.760", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was sich in der Region an Alternativen entwickeln k\u00f6nnte. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.400", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als Politik sind wir jederzeit zu Gespr\u00e4chen bereit."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.840", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Standortschlie\u00dfungen m\u00fcssen vermieden werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.160", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich hoffe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.000", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Sozialpartner aufeinander zugehen und in fairem Dialog Chancen f\u00fcr die Mitarbeiterinnen und Mitarbeiter aufzeigen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.200", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das gilt f\u00fcr Siemens, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.760", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "General Electric, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "230.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "236.000", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bombardier genauso wie f\u00fcr Air Berlin und die M\u00fcller-Homann-Gruppe."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "236.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.800", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herzlichen Dank und Gl\u00fcck auf. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.920", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich w\u00fcnsche Ihnen ein frohes Weihnachtsfest und ein hoffentlich erfolgreiches und friedliches neues Jahr."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "248.400", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herzlichen Dank.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "248.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.480", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als letzter Redner: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "253.000", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kollege Peter Wei\u00df von der CDU/CSU-Fraktion."
   ]
  }
 ]
}